  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4555987">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4555987/" class="title-link">美国政治的另一部分</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4555987"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/46841021/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u46841021-9.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/46841021/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Ropemark</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-12-30"
      class="main-meta">2010-12-30 16:39:26</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4555987_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  书中关于所谓美国权贵阶层的说法我并不太接受，虽然存在这样一个阶层，但是其政治表现差异很大。来自这一阶层的罗斯福，其平民主义倾向远远超过出身比较低的前任，来自铁路大亨家族的哈里曼也是如此。  最为有趣的部分是关于麦克纳马拉，这位通用的前总经理，如何用大企业管理...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_4555987_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_4555987_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1251286">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1251286/" class="title-link">Gap Filling</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1251286"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1054983/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1054983/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">holden</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2007-12-02"
      class="main-meta">2007-12-02 12:23:50</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1251286_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  Gap Filling Pls choose the best sentence from the list after the passage to fill each of the gaps in the text.           Selling out to the Students  University faculties involve themselves unwittingly in the destruction of the university when they bow to a...

